Package svc

Class Result

java.lang.Object
svc.Result
Direct Known Subclasses:
CreateGameResult, ListGamesResult, LoginResult
public class Result extends Object
Result class is a super class for all the result classes. This includes the variables message and code which will be utilized by all the subclasses. It manages the default messages for each status code as well.
